threads.title: 820-3332-a missing P3V3GPU_EN
threads.message: I have 820-3332-a water damaged board has orange light but doesn't turn on. After measuring the power rails I've find out that i have few power rails missing P3V3GPU_EN,  P1V8GPU_EN,  GPUVCORE_EN and i think they all coming from the SMC if im right ????
